Dorsal, lateral and front view of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jordal" authorityYear="2022" box="[689,977,1944,1968]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Pseudomicracis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="335" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vitrioculata">
<emphasis box="[689,977,1944,1968]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="335">Pseudomicracis vitrioculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
male holotype (20, 23, 26); 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jordal" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Pseudomicracis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="335" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pilosa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="335">Pseudomicracis pilosa</emphasis>
